  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to The Cabin Factory - as a newly hired Cabin Inspector your job is to inspect the cabins and determine whether or not they are haunted. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspect the whole cabin:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If haunted, turn back immediately and press 'danger'.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Is safe, press 'clear'.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cabin Factory is a short horror anomaly-hunting experience (~60 minutes) inspired by liminal spaces and psychological horror walking simulators, like '<i>The Exit 8</i>', '<i>Pools'</i>, and their virtual predecessor, '<i>P.T.</i>'.</p>",
